Dear All,

We are pleased to announce the following international event (school + =
conference) on topos theory, which will take place in Como from 24 to 29 =
June 2018.

We hope to see you in Como.

Best regards,
Olivia Caramello (on behalf of the Scientific and Organizing Committees) =



