* Short communications *
----------------------------------

There is room for a few short communications (20-25 minutes long); if =
you want to submit a one-page abstract for a short talk at the =
conference, please upload=20
it while registering on the conference website before the 15th of April.

* Financial support for students and young researchers *
-------------------------------------------------------------------------=
--

There is a limited number of travel grants (or registration fee =
exemptions) for attending this event available for deserving students =
and young researchers who are not funded by their own institutions. If =
interested in obtaining such a grant, please send a request to the =
address mailto:tcsc@lakecomoschool.org before the 15th of April, =
attaching a Curriculum Vitae and a supporting letter by a senior =
mathematician (e.g. your Ph.D. supervisor).

* Registration and contact *
------------------------------------

Registration information is available at the conference webpage=20
http://tcsc.lakecomoschool.org/registration/=20

If you have any queries please send them to the conference e-mail =
address
tcsc@lakecomoschool.org =20


